Type shortcut:
ctrl+l  = clear
ctrl+d  = exit/logout
ctrl+a  = move to the begining of the current line
crtl+e  = move curture to the end of the current line
ctrl+u = delete the entire string of the current line
ctrl+z = pose the porecess 

 
